                        </provenance>
                        <acquisition>Purchased by <persName key="person_f6379" role="dnr" change="#prov-markup">Enriqueta Rylands</persName> in 1901 from <persName key="person_9985420" role="fmo" change="#prov-markup">James Ludovic Lindsay, 26th Earl of Crawford</persName>, for the John Rylands Library.</acquisition>
